OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with some outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain. Further rain at times overnight,
OL,8,Fmostly affecting northern areas, with
OL,9,Fsouthern Aberdeenshire having more in
OL,10,Fthe way of dry spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA cloudy start with some rain,
OL,13,Fmainly in the north. Then becoming dry
OL,14,Fand brightening up with some hazy
OL,15,Fsunshine at times.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMainly
OL,18,Fcloudy, patchy rain on Tuesday, some
OL,19,Fbright spells. Wednesday and Thursday
OL,20,Fwill be dry with sunny spells and
OL,21,Fbecoming very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
